==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbe
<hw>Un*be"</hw> <pr>(⟦ucr⟧n*b⟦emac⟧")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>be</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause not to be; to
cause to be another.</def> <mark>[Obs. & R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How oft, with danger of the field beset,⟦br⟧
Or with home mutinies, would he <qex>unbe</qex>⟦br⟧
Himself!</q> <rj><qau>Old Play.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbear</ent>⟦br⟧
